- ajout de son sur la video :
    - https://github.com/myshell-ai/MeloTTS pour english, spanish, french, chinese, japanese and korean
        You can use moviepy library to do that. Behind the scenes, it uses ffmpeg to merge audio and video.

        import moviepy.editor as mp

        video_path = 'Path to video file'
        audio_path = 'Path to audio file'
        output_path = 'Path to output video+audio file'

        video = mp.VideoFileClip(video_path)
        audio = mp.AudioFileClip(audio_path)

        video = video.set_audio(audio)

        video.write_videofile(output_path)


